data.description: VACANT & MOVE IN READY!!! This ranch style home is nestled in the highly sought-after area of Masonboro Loop and is epitome of comfort and convenience! As you step inside, you'll be welcomed by an open living space centered around a cozy fireplace, creating the perfect atmosphere for family gatherings & relaxing. The thoughtful layout makes this residence ideal for a primary family home, with a spacious living area that come fully furnished, ready for you to move in and make memories. As you step through the back door into your own private spacious fenced-in yard complete with a delightful patio, ideal for grilling, entertaining, and enjoying all your favorite outdoor activities.Location is a standout feature of this property. Just a short 15-minute drive will take you to the pristine shores of Wrightsville Beach and Carolina Beach, making it easy to enjoy coastal living to the fullest. Additionally, you're conveniently situated near the Wilmington Municipal Golf Course, Masonboro Station, and Courtyard at Masonboro, offering a range of amenities and activities right at your doorstep. This home checks all the boxes for comfortable living in a prime location.
